# OPM Orientation Documents (Non-Normative)

This directory contains **non-normative orientation documents** for the Open Publication Model (OPM).

These documents introduce **no requirements** and carry **no normative authority**. Their purpose is to establish architectural boundaries, mental models, and expectations before reading the specifications.

Readers are strongly encouraged to read these documents **before** engaging with the Architectural Foundations or technical specifications.

The recommended reading order is indicated by file numbering.
